<text top="1146" left="1620" width="626" height="45" font="font0" id="p1_t129" reading_order_no="127" segment_no="1" tag_type="text">number—32  bits  in  all—requiring,  on </text>
<text top="1188" left="1608" width="637" height="50" font="font2" id="p1_t130" reading_order_no="128" segment_no="1" tag_type="text">average,  some  4  billion  spoofed  replies </text>
<text top="1234" left="1606" width="641" height="49" font="font1" id="p1_t131" reading_order_no="129" segment_no="1" tag_type="text">to  be  received.  Such  a  colossal  amount </text>
<text top="1280" left="1628" width="618" height="49" font="font1" id="p1_t132" reading_order_no="130" segment_no="1" tag_type="text">of  traffic  would  be  hard  to  conceal </text>
<text top="1326" left="1644" width="502" height="49" font="font1" id="p1_t133" reading_order_no="131" segment_no="1" tag_type="text">from  network  administrators. </text>
