<text top="1556" left="1817" width="428" height="49" font="font1" id="p1_t137" reading_order_no="135" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">and  hackers  appear  to  be </text>
<text top="1603" left="1816" width="303" height="47" font="font3" id="p1_t138" reading_order_no="136" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">testing  the  waters. </text>
