<text top="1789" left="1600" width="647" height="45" font="font0" id="p1_t142" reading_order_no="140" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">York  City,  says,  “I’ve  seen  reports  that </text>
<text top="1832" left="1605" width="642" height="47" font="font3" id="p1_t143" reading_order_no="141" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">it’s  started  to  happen  in  the  wild.”  But </text>
<text top="1878" left="1605" width="649" height="47" font="font3" id="p1_t144" reading_order_no="142" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">he  believes  that  DNS  cache  poison- </text>
