<text top="2107" left="1605" width="648" height="49" font="font1" id="p1_t149" reading_order_no="147" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">now  taking  appropriate  steps.  He  never- </text>
<text top="2156" left="1605" width="640" height="46" font="font4" id="p1_t150" reading_order_no="148" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">theless  cautions,  “It’s  one  of  the  more </text>
<text top="2203" left="1606" width="639" height="45" font="font0" id="p1_t151" reading_order_no="149" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">serious  problems  we’ve  seen,  because </text>
